    <remarks variants="5">
        <remark source-urls="2">
            <p>First Secretary and Consul of the Legation in Vietnam until September 1, 1952; loaned to Mutual Security Agency as Chief of the Mutual Security Agency (MSA) Mission at Saigon, September 1, 1952–July 5, 1953; detailed to National War College, July 5, 1953–June 20. 1954; thereafter; Counselor of the Embassy in India for Economic Affairs; also Counselor of the Embassy in Nepal for Economic Affairs from September 21, 1954.</p>
            <source-url>https://history.state.gov/historicaldocuments/frus1952-54v11p1/persons#p_BFP1</source-url>
